    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/20cc6bd9469188dd9d16c52f24fb7784.poster.avif?t=1742493493\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/20cc6bd9469188dd9d16c52f24fb7784.webm?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/20cc6bd9469188dd9d16c52f24fb7784.mp4?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简报</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您是生物和化学威胁防治团队的一员。您的使命是收集、隔离和交付未知物质或物体以进行进一步分析。您的团队即将被派往一座基于太空站的化学研发设施。在完全失去通讯之前，已经有多次动力核心故障的报告。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜索可疑物质并尽快将其送至安全地点。明智地管理您的能源：一切可能会在眨眼间变得一片漆黑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>环境。</i>明亮的环境、漆黑的黑暗和威胁性的应急灯光与逼真的图形和声音形成鲜明对比，确保了引人入胜的体验，让您保持紧张感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>持久威胁。</i>AI以始终存在并可触及的方式制作，规划行动并识别未知的干扰源。基于玩家的行动，它将决定玩家是否具有敌意。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/bd92b815de8b953f649437c1852b64ba.poster.avif?t=1742493493\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/bd92b815de8b953f649437c1852b64ba.webm?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/bd92b815de8b953f649437c1852b64ba.mp4?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>不同玩法。</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>站点能源有限，不知道能维持多久。<br><br><i>能源管理。</i> 通过错综复杂的走廊规划您的旅程。选择以电力为基准点亮站点的哪一部分，并使用个人设备照亮您的路途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>奖励制度。</i>如果以任何可能的方式完成任务，则将在玩家之间分配游戏内点数。<strong>多人游戏</strong> <br> <br><i>合作。</i>与最多4名玩家一起游玩。<i>团队合作。</i>以最大化奖励为目标分配您的责任。<i>兼容性。</i>NIKTOPHOBIA支持不同的输入类型，可以在VR和PC上一起游玩。查看系统要求以获取更多详情。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/91bc70af34169f7dfc5971f6bac957f7.poster.avif?t=1742493493\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/91bc70af34169f7dfc5971f6bac957f7.webm?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398680/extras/91bc70af34169f7dfc5971f6bac957f7.mp4?t=1742493493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
